    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine runs smoothly and starts reliably every time, with no major mechanical issues to report. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only minor wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though there are a few small stone chips on the hood and light scratches near the door handles from normal use. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner.",
